Steps to install SASS:

1. Install Node.js version 20.16 using nvm:
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   
2. Exit and reopen terminal

3. Install and use Node.js 20.16:
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16

4. Install SASS globally:
   $ npm install -g sass@1.77.4

5. Verify installation:
   $ sass --version

Alternative installation (if you have Node.js already):
   $ npm install sass -v 3.7.4
